com.myscript.atk.mltw.model

Class Word

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.myscript.atk.mltw.model.Word

  • public class Word
extends Object
    Represents a word inside the widget. It contains information about the text representation of the word as well as its candidates and position in the widget.
